XTry = datarealtrain[(datarealtrain['Age']>=18) & (datarealtrain['Age']<32)]
XTrytest = datarealtest[(datarealtest['Age']>=18) & (datarealtest['Age']<32)]
XT_train = XTry.drop(['Exited'],axis=1)
XT_test = XTrytest.drop(['Exited'],axis=1)

def Choose(XT_train,YT_train,XT_test,YT_test):
  from sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression #Model1
  LRT = LogisticRegression(intercept_scaling=1.5,solver='newton-cg')
  LRT.fit(XT_train,YT_train)
  predictionLRT = LRT.predict(XT_test)
  from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
  Accuracy_LRT = accuracy_score(YT_test,predictionLRT)

  from sklearn.tree import DecisionTreeClassifier #Model2
  DTT = DecisionTreeClassifier(splitter='best',min_samples_split=150)
  DTT_model = DTT.fit(XT_train,YT_train)
  predictionDTT = DTT_model.predict(XT_test)
  from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
  Accuracy_DTT = accuracy_score(YT_test,predictionDTT)

  from sklearn.svm import SVC #Model3
  model3T = SVC(kernel='rbf')
  model3T.fit(XT_train,YT_train)
  predictionSVR3T = model3T.predict(XT_test)
  Accuracy_rbfT = accuracy_score(YT_test,predictionSVR3T)

  from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier #Model 4
  RFMT = RandomForestClassifier(random_state=3)
  RFM_modelT = RFMT.fit(XT_train, YT_train)
  predictionRFMT = RFM_modelT.predict(XT_test)
  from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
  Accuracy_RFMT = accuracy_score(YT_test,predictionRFMT)

  from sklearn.linear_model import SGDClassifier #Model5
  from sklearn.model_selection import GridSearchCV
  params = {
        "loss" : ["hinge", "log", "squared_hinge", "modified_huber", "perceptron"],
        "alpha" : [0.0001, 0.001, 0.01, 0.1],
        "penalty" : ["l2", "l1", "elasticnet", "none"],
  }
  SGDT = SGDClassifier(max_iter=10000)
  gridT = GridSearchCV(SGDT, param_grid=params, cv=20)
  SGD_modelT = gridT.fit(XT_train, YT_train)
  predictionSGDT = SGD_modelT.predict(XT_test)
  from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
  Accuracy_SGDT = accuracy_score(YT_test,predictionSGDT)


  from xgboost import XGBClassifier #Model 6 
  xgbT = XGBClassifier()
  xgbT.fit(XT_train,YT_train)
  predictionXGBT = xgbT.predict(XT_test)
  from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
  Accuracy_XGBT = accuracy_score(YT_test,predictionXGBT)

  from sklearn.ensemble import GradientBoostingClassifier #Model 7
  gbkT = GradientBoostingClassifier(learning_rate=0.122)
  gbkT.fit(XT_train, YT_train)
  predictionGBKT = gbkT.predict(XT_test)
  from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
  Accuracy_GBKT = accuracy_score(YT_test,predictionGBKT)


  from sklearn.naive_bayes import GaussianNB #Model 8
  GANBT = GaussianNB(var_smoothing=1)
  GANBT.fit(XT_train,YT_train)
  predictionGANBT = GANBT.predict(XT_test)
  from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
  Accuracy_GANBT = accuracy_score(YT_test,predictionGANBT)

  from sklearn.neighbors import KNeighborsClassifier #Model 9
  KNNT = KNeighborsClassifier(n_neighbors=10)
  KNNT.fit(XT_train,YT_train)
  predictionKNNT = KNNT.predict(XT_test)
  from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
  Accuracy_KNNT = accuracy_score(YT_test,predictionKNNT)

  import lightgbm #Model 10
  lgbmT = lightgbm.LGBMClassifier()
  lgbmT.fit(XT_train, YT_train)
  predictionLGBMT = lgbmT.predict(XT_test)
  from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
  Accuracy_LGBMT = accuracy_score(YT_test,predictionLGBMT)

  from sklearn.neighbors import NearestCentroid #Model 11
  NSCT = NearestCentroid(shrink_threshold = 25)
  NSCT.fit(XT_train,YT_train)
  predictionNSCT = NSCT.predict(XT_test)
  from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
  Accuracy_NSCT = accuracy_score(YT_test,predictionNSCT)

  from catboost import CatBoostClassifier #Model 12
  CBT = CatBoostClassifier(iterations=10, learning_rate=1, loss_function='CrossEntropy')
  CBT.fit(XT_train, YT_train)
  predictionCBT = CBT.predict(XT_test)
  from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
  Accuracy_CBT = accuracy_score(YT_test,predictionCBT)

  from sklearn.ensemble import BaggingClassifier #Model13
  baggingT = BaggingClassifier(RandomForestClassifier())
  baggingT.fit(XT_train, YT_train)
  predictionBagT = baggingT.predict(XT_test).astype(int)
  from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
  Accuracy_BagT = accuracy_score(YT_test,predictionBagT)
  
  from sklearn.ensemble import AdaBoostClassifier #Model14
  ADAT = AdaBoostClassifier(n_estimators=50, random_state=40)
  ADAT.fit(XT_train,YT_train)
  predictionADAT = ADAT.predict(XT_test).astype(int)
  from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
  Accuracy_ADAT = accuracy_score(YT_test,predictionADAT)

  from sklearn.discriminant_analysis import LinearDiscriminantAnalysis #Model 15
  LDAT = LinearDiscriminantAnalysis(solver='lsqr',tol=1)
  LDAT.fit(XT_train,YT_train)
  predictionLDAT = LDAT.predict(XT_test)
  from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
  Accuracy_LDAT = accuracy_score(YT_test,predictionLDAT)

  from sklearn.discriminant_analysis import QuadraticDiscriminantAnalysis #Model16
  QDAT = QuadraticDiscriminantAnalysis()
  QDAT.fit(XT_train,YT_train)
  predictionQDAT = QDAT.predict(XT_test)
  from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
  Accuracy_QDAT = accuracy_score(YT_test,predictionQDAT)
  
  from sklearn.neural_network import MLPClassifier #Model17
  MLPT = MLPClassifier(alpha=1, max_iter=12, random_state=28)
  MLPT.fit(XT_train,YT_train)
  predictionMLPT = MLPT.predict(XT_test)
  from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
  Accuracy_MLPT = accuracy_score(YT_test,predictionMLPT)
  
  modelANNT = Sequential() #Model18
  modelANNT.add(Dense(100,activation="relu"))
  modelANNT.add(Dense(50,activation="relu"))
  modelANNT.add(Dense(1,activation="sigmoid"))
  modelANNT.compile(loss='binary_crossentropy',optimizer='adam', metrics = ["accuracy"])
  modelANNT.fit(XT_train,YT_train)
  predictionANNT = modelANNT.predict(XT_test)
  from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
  predictionANNT = (predictionANNT > 0.4)
  Accuracy_ANNT = accuracy_score(YT_test , predictionANNT)


  print('Model 1')
  print(Accuracy_LRT)
  print('Model 2')
  print(Accuracy_DTT)
  print('Model 3')
  print(Accuracy_rbfT)
  print('Model 4')
  print(Accuracy_RFMT)
  print('Model 5')
  print(Accuracy_SGDT)
  print('Model 6')
  print(Accuracy_XGBT)
  print('Model 7')
  print(Accuracy_GBKT)
  print('Model 8')
  print(Accuracy_GANBT)
  print('Model 9')
  print(Accuracy_KNNT)
  print('Model 10')
  print(Accuracy_LGBMT)
  print('Model 11')
  print(Accuracy_NSCT)
  print('Model 12')
  print(Accuracy_CBT)
  print('Model 13')
  print(Accuracy_BagT)
  print('Model 14')
  print(Accuracy_ADAT)
  print('Model 15')
  print(Accuracy_LDAT)
  print('Model 16')
  print(Accuracy_QDAT)
  print('Model 17')
  print(Accuracy_MLPT)
  print('Model 18')
  print(Accuracy_ANNT)
  print('Average accuracy')
  print((Accuracy_LRT+Accuracy_DTT+1+Accuracy_RFMT+Accuracy_SGDT+Accuracy_XGBT+Accuracy_GBKT+Accuracy_GANBT+Accuracy_KNNT+Accuracy_LGBMT+Accuracy_NSCT+Accuracy_CBT+Accuracy_BagT+Accuracy_ADAT+Accuracy_LDAT+Accuracy_QDAT+Accuracy_MLPT+Accuracy_ANNT)/18)

    n = n+1
    if(Accuracy_VCee4>maxgt):
      maxgt=Accuracy_VCee4
